lgp.core.evolution.training

Class SequentialTrainingJob<TProgram,TOutput extends Output<TProgram>>

  • TrainingJob
    • lgp.core.evolution.training.SequentialTrainingJob<TProgram,TOutput>

  • public class SequentialTrainingJob<TProgram,TOutput extends Output<TProgram>>
extends TrainingJob

    Represents an asynchronous sequential training operation.

    When using the built-in class SequentialTrainer implementations in an asynchronous manner, a class SequentialTrainingJob will be returned which provides mechanisms to retrieve the class TrainingResult and subscribe to interface TrainingUpdateMessages sent from the class SequentialTrainer.

    See Also:
    class SequentialTrainer, class SequentialTrainingJob, class TrainingResult, interface TrainingUpdateMessage, class SequentialTrainer

      • result

        public java.lang.Object result(kotlin.coroutines.experimental.Continuation<? super lgp.core.evolution.training.TrainingResult<TProgram,TOutput>> p)

        Retrieves the result of training.

        If the job has already been completed then the function will not suspend. Otherwise, the function will suspend until training is complete.

      • subscribeToUpdates

        public void subscribeToUpdates(kotlin.jvm.functions.Function1<? super lgp.core.evolution.training.TrainingMessages.ProgressUpdate<TProgram,TOutput>,kotlin.Unit> callback)

        Subscribes a callback function that will be executed each time a interface TrainingUpdateMessage is received.

        The callback will be passed the message and allow the subscriber to use the value as it wishes.

        Parameters:
        callback - The function to execute when a interface TrainingUpdateMessage is received.
